    "shortBio": "AI consultant and ML engineer with 9+ years of experience delivering generative AI consulting, LLM applications, and RAG systems that drive measurable business outcomes. I specialize in AI strategy consulting, AI automation, and full-stack product delivery using Python, FastAPI, Next.js, TypeScript, and cloud-native architecture.",
    "fullBioParagraphs": [
      "I am an AI consultant and ML engineer with 9+ years of hands-on experience designing and delivering production-grade AI systems for enterprises and growth-focused teams. My work spans AI consulting services, machine learning consulting services, and full-stack product engineering built for reliability, speed, and business impact.",
      "I specialize in generative AI consulting services, LLM consulting, and RAG development services, helping teams turn complex ideas into practical products. This includes AI agent development services, AI chatbot development services, and AI integration services that improve decision-making, automate workflows, and reduce operational friction.",
      "From an engineering perspective, I build end-to-end solutions across data pipelines, model orchestration, backend APIs, and modern web interfaces. My core stack includes Python, FastAPI, SQL, Next.js, React, and TypeScript, with a focus on observability, performance, security, and maintainable architecture.",
      "I approach every engagement with an outcome-first mindset: understand the business context deeply, design the right system, and ship with clear metrics for success. If you are looking for an AI consultant in India for enterprise AI consulting, AI transformation consulting, or product-focused delivery, I bring strategy and execution together."
    ],
