      "coverImageAlt": "AI-powered blog assistant using RAG architecture for content retrieval",
      "featured": true,
      "coverImage": "/uploads/cms/blog-1776487712818-d45d5bbe.png",
      "impactSummary": "Built an AI-powered assistant that enables users to query blog content in natural language, improving content discoverability and increasing user engagement. Reduced manual search effort and enabled intelligent content recommendations.",
      "problemStatement": "Users often struggle to find relevant information across multiple blog posts, leading to poor engagement and higher bounce rates. Traditional search lacks contextual understanding and fails to provide precise answers.",
      "solutionApproach": "Designed and implemented a Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) system that indexes blog content into vector embeddings. User queries are semantically matched against stored embeddings, and relevant content is retrieved and passed to a language model to generate contextual answers.\n\nIntegrated backend APIs for query processing and deployed a chatbot interface for seamless user interaction.",
